Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好難畫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道挑簡單一點的畫就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.64,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞爾，你連畫畫都很行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.47,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有人在看這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在看你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看的人是妳啦，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也真是辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好不容易鼓起勇氣\N想向小櫻表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果被小可破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要什麼時候跟她說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不想告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.38,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我只想著\N一定要告訴她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事我得先處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.19,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第60話 小櫻與她重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.43,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我有喜歡的人之前\N要當莓鈴的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.37,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把現在的心情告訴莓鈴，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上打電話給她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說有事要當面告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她問我不能在電話裡告訴她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她想當面告訴她\N她說她知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好跟莓鈴談過\N然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候要去見莓鈴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放寒假我要回香港\N到時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了那麼久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.25,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打電話之後\N她就馬上來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴怎麼可能等到放寒假…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼突然來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來辦點事\N對不對？小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要在這裡待多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要上學\N所以明天就得趕回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那今天呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放學後\N我們一起去玩好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，不過\N妳是來辦事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能沒空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子，木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那放學後在校門口見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾，我今天要去學游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去學鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要替我們多陪莓鈴聊聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟寺田老師打聲招呼\N待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，我馬上就回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？我現在打得正過癮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然這時候打來，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可，你又在打電動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是小櫻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一下我就要破四億分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要跟莓鈴出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會晚點回去\N要記得打開電鍋的開關喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭丫頭來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她說明天就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我今天想跟她聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴那個臭丫頭一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我要讓她看到我超酷的樣子\N叫她別嚇得腿軟了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了電鍋喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我打擾妳打電話了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，我剛剛講完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.73,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才班上來了一位\N我沒見過的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮長長的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫作李莓鈴\N是我們以前的同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一學期結束時\N她回香港去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐的就是她的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是小狼的表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好今天放學後一起去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天色暗了會比較危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼笑嘻嘻的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為能見到妳，我很高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這點小事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以見到妳\N我真的非常非常高興嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.22,0:08:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，能再見到妳我也很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那麼最後\N妳成為庫洛牌的新主人囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是怪事仍繼續再發生，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題嗎？\N因為木之本總是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼是呆呆的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.68,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆呆的就是呆呆的啊\N這不需要解釋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好像很輕的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼解釋才好呢\N日文應該是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要今天告訴莓鈴嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我的心意已決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不說的話\N就等於是對莓鈴毀約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要遵守我跟莓鈴的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像你的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.04,0:09:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你是這樣的人\N莓鈴才會喜歡上你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說\N又開了一間新的果汁店喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的綜合果汁好好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們到那裡聊聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有庫洛先生的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有股強大魔力的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是妳剛才說的怪事，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法對付那個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下怎麼打得完嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡\N要是能讓他們不動的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若用樹牌，無法一次捉住它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若用時牌，以我的魔力來說\N也不知道可以暫停多久時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天氣這麼冷，怎麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那個啦，那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在溜冰場捉到的那張牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將大家冰凍起來的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凍牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘊藏星星力量的鑰匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯現真正的神力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.67,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據契約，小櫻命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除封印！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛創造的庫洛牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄舊有姿態\N重新轉生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以新主人，小櫻之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「凍」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧莓鈴想到這個好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，小櫻\N有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是莓鈴幫了我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，莓鈴妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，妳受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事，我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是靠香港女孩的建議\N而讓他們得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果不能去喝果汁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼剛才都沒人經過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明鬧成那個樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是移動企鵝的人搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在回想起來\N以前發生怪事的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近也都沒人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事做得到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是魔力很強的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔力很強的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼突然這麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼事\N請妳都要想起我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴\N妳明天搭幾點的飛機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上10點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，我們要上學\N不能去送妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以後再見面不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本跟香港就像在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.55,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有了最喜歡的人\N我們約好了要告訴妳，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…木之本嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫她小櫻嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.78,0:18:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會叫女生的名字\N除了你姊姊之外就只有我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們取消婚約吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去大道寺家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天沒跟她說到話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我送妳去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，我搭計程車去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我會從大道寺家直接去機場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她靜一靜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…\N我是全世界最喜歡小狼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕不會輸給任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更讓我生氣的事是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.99,0:19:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣\N我還是不會討厭木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼會喜歡上木之本\N這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.80,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是這麼想的\N可是我哭又是另外一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要哭到眼睛融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要哭到死\N哭到不會再為小狼而哭為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛腫腫的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會，妳跟平常一樣可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.94,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你站在那裡幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來送我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴木之本了嗎？\N說你喜歡她了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒嗎？真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.44,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本那種人\N你不說她是不會知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不選這麼可愛的我\N而選了木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.08,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們不好好相處\N我絕不原諒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.12,0:21:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放假的時候要回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴小姐真是心地善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴寄信來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.78,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也收到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她給妳的信上寫些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.09,0:22:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說“對不起弄濕了妳的膝蓋”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳的信上寫什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.36,0:22:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說我呆呆的\N所以要我多看清楚一點四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.40,0:22:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說我有很多事都沒注意到\N所以她很擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.51,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有最後的這個，妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.78,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼唸，是什麼意思\N我雖然不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信一定是一句好話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得好高興喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.61,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝遲鈍的小狼\N趕快表白得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在香港的天空下為你祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.22,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的朋友，李小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.20,0:24:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕節就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.97,0:24:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟哥哥約好\N要一起去買聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有庫洛先生的氣息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.71,0:24:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，我得快點趕去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.24,0:24:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是\N我跟哥哥約好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛魔法使\N「小櫻、庫洛牌與禮物」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.45,0:24:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也與小櫻一起\N解除封印！
